title: Venison Shank And Chestnut Mushroom Suet Pudding
summary: This recipe serves 6 and costs $6.92 per serving. One serving contains 909 calories, 42g of protein, and 46g of fat. Only a few people made this recipe, and 4 would say it hit the spot. A mixture of sugar, sherry vinegar, stocks of celery, and a handful of other ingredients are all it takes to make this recipe so scrumptious. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes around 3 hours and 30 minutes. With a spoonacular score of 73%, this dish is pretty good. Similar recipes include Wild venison, field mushroom & ale pudding, Mushroom and chestnut pie, and Mushroom & Chestnut Soup.
